Functional Requirements:
- Submit long URL -> receive a shortened version: check
- Access original URL by using shortened one: check

Non Functional Requirements:
- Should ensure uniqueness for short codes (no 2 long URLs can map to the same short URL)
- The redirection should occur with minimal delay (< 100ms)
- Should be reliable and available 99.99%
- Should be scale to support 1B shortened URLs and 100M DAU

UI/UX (dev):
- Show all the urls in the storage

